  Lines:
  - Character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3824985fb57bacf46b1317dcff8cbab6, type: 3}
    Text: "Bon bah, t'as gagn\xE9\u2026"
  - Character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3824985fb57bacf46b1317dcff8cbab6, type: 3}
    Text: "J'aurais jamais cru perdre de cette fa\xE7on."
  - Character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: b947339f7387f104dbca0f323ffa7b4e, type: 3}
    Text: "T'inqui\xE8te, ils \xE9taient sympas ces jeux."
  - Character: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 3824985fb57bacf46b1317dcff8cbab6, type: 3}
    Text: "Si tu le dis\u2026 bon, tiens, je te donne ma console comme promis."
